<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New York Residential Lease Agreement</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
      font-size: 11pt;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #000;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 18pt;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .section {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 12pt;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .info-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .info-item {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .info-label {
      font-weight: bold;
      display: inline-block;
      min-width: 120px;
    }
    .tenants-list {
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .tenant-item {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      padding: 10px;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      border-left: 3px solid #333;
    }
    .signature-section {
      margin-top: 40px;
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }
    .signature-line {
      border-top: 1px solid #000;
      margin-top: 60px;
      width: 300px;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .terms {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    .terms ol {
      margin-left: 20px;
    }
    .terms li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .ny-notice {
      background-color: #e3f2fd;
      border: 2px solid #2196f3;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    @media print {
      body {
        padding: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>NEW YORK RESIDENTIAL LEASE AGREEMENT</h1>
    <p><strong>{{organizationName}}</strong></p>
  </div>

  <div class="ny-notice">
    <strong>NEW YORK-SPECIFIC NOTICE:</strong> This lease is subject to New York Real Property Law and local rent stabilization/control laws. 
    Tenant has rights under the New York State Tenant Protection Act.
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">1. PARTIES</div>
    <p>
      This Lease Agreement ("Lease") is entered into on <strong>{{generatedDate}}</strong>, 
      between <strong>{{organizationName}}</strong> ("Landlord") and the following tenant(s) ("Tenant"):
    </p>
    <div class="tenants-list">
      {{#each tenants}}
      <div class="tenant-item">
        <strong>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</strong>
        {{#if isPrimary}}<em>(Primary Tenant)</em>{{/if}}<br>
        {{#if email}}Email: {{email}}{{/if}}{{#if phone}} | Phone: {{phone}}{{/if}}
      </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">2. PROPERTY</div>
    <div class="info-grid">
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">Property:</span> {{propertyName}}
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">Address:</span> {{propertyAddress}}
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">Unit:</span> {{unitName}}
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">State:</span> New York (NY)
      </div>
      {{#if bedrooms}}
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">Bedrooms:</span> {{bedrooms}}
      </div>
      {{/if}}
      {{#if bathrooms}}
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">Bathrooms:</span> {{bathrooms}}
      </div>
      {{/if}}
      {{#if squareFeet}}
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">Square Feet:</span> {{squareFeet}}
      </div>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">3. TERM</div>
    <p>
      The term of this Lease shall commence on <strong>{{date startDate}}</strong> and shall terminate on 
      <strong>{{date endDate}}</strong>, unless sooner terminated in accordance with the terms of this Lease.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-title">4. RENT</div>
    <div class="info-grid">
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">Monthly Rent:</span> {{currency rentAmount}}
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">Rent Due Date:</span> Day {{rentDueDay}} of each month
      </div>
      {{#if depositAmount}}
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-label">Security Deposit:</span> {{currency depositAmount}}
      </div>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
    <p>
      Rent shall be due and payable in advance on the {{rentDueDay}} day of each month during the term of this Lease. 
      If rent is not received by the {{rentDueDay}} day of the month, Tenant shall be in default of this Lease.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>New York Law:</strong> Under New York Real Property Law, rent is due on the date specified in this lease. 
      Security deposits are subject to New York General Obligations Law Section 7-103.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="section terms">
    <div class="section-title">5. TERMS AND CONDITIONS</div>
    <ol>
      <li>
        <strong>Use of Premises:</strong> Tenant shall use the premises solely as a private residence and for no other purpose.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Warranty of Habitability:</strong> Landlord warrants that the premises are fit for human habitation and will maintain the premises in such condition. 
        Tenant may withhold rent or seek remedies for breach of warranty of habitability under New York Real Property Law.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Maintenance:</strong> Tenant shall maintain the premises in good condition and promptly notify Landlord of any needed repairs.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Alterations:</strong> Tenant shall not make any alterations, additions, or improvements to the premises without Landlord's prior written consent.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Utilities:</strong> Tenant shall be responsible for all utilities unless otherwise specified in writing.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Pets:</strong> No pets are allowed on the premises without Landlord's prior written consent.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Security Deposit:</strong> The security deposit shall be held by Landlord in accordance with New York General Obligations Law Section 7-103. 
        The deposit may be applied to any damages, unpaid rent, or other charges owed by Tenant.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Rent Stabilization/Control:</strong> This property may be subject to New York rent stabilization or rent control laws. 
        Tenant is advised to check with the New York State Division of Housing and Community Renewal (DHCR) for applicable regulations.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Default:</strong> If Tenant fails to pay rent or breaches any term of this Lease, Landlord may terminate this Lease 
        in accordance with New York Real Property Actions and Proceedings Law and pursue all available remedies.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Governing Law:</strong> This Lease shall be governed by the laws of the State of New York.
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <div class="signature-section">
    <p>IN WITNESS WHEREOF, the parties have executed this Lease as of the date first written above.</p>
    
    <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
      <div style="display: inline-block; width: 45%; vertical-align: top;">
        <p><strong>LANDLORD:</strong></p>
        <p>{{organizationName}}</p>
        <div class="signature-line"></div>
        <p style="margin-top: 5px; font-size: 9pt;">Signature</p>
        <div class="signature-line" style="margin-top: 20px;"></div>
        <p style="margin-top: 5px; font-size: 9pt;">Date</p>
      </div>
      
      <div style="display: inline-block; width: 45%; vertical-align: top; margin-left: 5%;">
        <p><strong>TENANT(S):</strong></p>
        {{#each tenants}}
        <p>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</p>
        <div class="signature-line"></div>
        <p style="margin-top: 5px; font-size: 9pt;">Signature</p>
        <div class="signature-line" style="margin-top: 20px;"></div>
        <p style="margin-top: 5px; font-size: 9pt;">Date</p>
        {{#unless @last}}<br><br>{{/unless}}
        {{/each}}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

